2\"|\u2013||38||1\n|-\n|[[Burnley F.C.|Burnley]]||[[2001\u201302 Burnley F.C. season|2001\u201302]]||First Division||6||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||6||0\n|-\n|[[Gansu Tianma F.C.|Gansu Tianma]]||2003||[[China League One]]||4||2||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||4||2\n|-\n|[[Boston United F.C.|Boston United]]||[[2004\u201305 Boston United F.C. season|2004\u201305]]||[[Football League Two|League Two]]||4||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||5||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total<ref>{{harvnb|Gascoigne|2004|p=356}}</ref>\n!388||83||28||12||37||13||15||2||468||110\n|}\n\n===International===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n|colspan=\"3\"|[[England national football team|England national team]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|1988||2||0\n|-\n|1989||4||1\n|-\n|1990||13||1\n|-\n|1991||1||0\n|-\n|1992||2||2\n|-\n|1993||6||2\n|-\n|1994||1||0\n|-\n|1995||6||0\n|-\n|1996||11||3\n|-\n|1997||8||1\n|-\n|1998||3||0\n|-\n!Total<ref name=\"rsssfint\">{{cite web |url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/gascoigne-intl.html |title=Paul John Gascoigne \u2013 International Appearances |publisher=Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation |date=15 January 2006 |accessdate=20 November 2014}}</ref>||57||10\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n:''Scores and results list England's goal tally first.<ref name=\"rsssfint\" />''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Result !! Competition !! Scored\n|-\n| 1 || 26 April 1989 || [[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Wembley Stadium]], [[London]], England || {{fb|ALB}} || 5\u20130 || [[1990 FIFA World Cup qualification|1990 World Cup qualifier]] || 1\n|-\n| 2 || 25 April 1990 || [[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Wembley Stadium]], [[London]], England || {{fb|TCH}} || 4\u20132 || Friendly || 1\n|-\n| 3, 4 || 18 November 1992 || [[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Wembley Stadium]], [[London]], England || {{fb|TUR}} || 4\u20130 || [[1994 FIFA World Cup qualification|1994 